:45',NULL,'approved'),(64,'Malibu\'s Burger','Burger','Malibu\'s Burger in San Francisco delivers a fun, indulgent take on classic American comfort food. Known for its stacked burgers, crispy fries, and creamy milkshakes, the menu is designed for maximum satisfaction. Creative toppings and hearty portions elevate the experience, while the lively, modern setting makes it a popular choice for casual dining, late-night cravings, or a quick bite with friends.','326 23rd Street','San Francisco',NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(65,'Osha Thai Express','Thai','Osha Thai Express brings the vibrant flavors of Thai cuisine into a convenient fast-casual format without sacrificing depth or authenticity. Signature dishes like pad Thai, pumpkin curry, and basil chicken are packed with aromatic herbs and bold spices. Perfect for a quick lunch or takeout, it offers a flavorful escape with every bite while maintaining the quality associated with the Osha name.','326 23rd Street','San Francisco',NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(66,'Lo Coco\'s','Italian','Lo Coco\'s is a Berkeley institution known for its warm hospitality and authentic Sicilian cooking. Founded by Giovanni Lo Coco, the restaurant carries forward family recipes that highlight rich sauces, hearty pastas, and rustic pizzas. The cozy, welcoming atmosphere makes it feel like dining in someone\'s home, while the generous portions and classic flavors keep guests returning for a true taste of tradition.','1400 Shattuck Avenue','Berkeley',NULL,NULL,'+1-510-843-3745',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(67,'Saul\'s Deli','Jewish','Saul\'s Deli is a cornerstone of Berkeley\'s food scene, offering a classic Jewish deli experience filled with nostalgia and flavor. Known for its towering pastrami sandwiches, house-made bagels, and comforting matzo ball soup, it blends tradition with a lively neighborhood atmosphere. Whether for breakfast, lunch, or brunch, it is a place where hearty portions and familiar flavors create a deeply satisfying experience.','1475 Shattuck Avenue','Berkeley',NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(68,'Ijo Izakaya','Japanese','Ijo Izakaya captures the essence of a traditional Japanese pub with a menu centered on small plates, fresh seafood, and comforting dishes. Guests can enjoy everything from sashimi and yakitori to rice bowls and sake in a cozy, relaxed setting. The inviting atmosphere encourages sharing and conversation, making it a great spot for casual gatherings and late-night bites in Berkeley.','1463 Shattuck Avenue','Berkeley',NULL,NULL,'+1-510-6795200',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(69,'Kirala 2','Japanese','Kirala 2 offers a simple yet satisfying Japanese dining experience focused on fresh sushi and reliable service. The menu includes a wide variety of rolls, nigiri, and bento-style meals that cater to both quick lunches and casual dinners. Its laid-back atmosphere and consistent quality make it a dependable choice for those seeking approachable Japanese cuisine in San Francisco.','Various Locations','San Francisco',NULL,NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',NULL,'approved'),(70,'Flavia','Italian','Flavia is a charming Berkeley restaurant that blends cozy ambiance with refined Italian cuisine. Known for its handmade pastas, rich sauces, and thoughtfully prepared dishes, it offers a dining experience that feels both intimate and elevated. The warm setting and attention to detail make it ideal for date nights, special occasions, or simply enjoying a leisurely meal with great food and wine.','1511 Shattuck Avenue','Berkeley',NULL,NULL,'+1-510-629-2030',NULL,NULL,NULL,'4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2026-03-20 01:45:45',